    "我一边进出，一边亲吻她。她将呻吟声吐进我的嘴里。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:511
translate chinese lisa12b_05953c2a:

    # "We make love, both of us just wanting to make the other feel as good as possible."
    "我们做爱，彼此都只想让对方获得最大的快感。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:516
translate chinese lisa12b_1a66d65e:

    # "Once we start though, we don't stop."
    "不过一旦开始，我们就停不下来。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:520
translate chinese lisa12b_fba43f50:

    # "When I get tired, she takes over."
    "当我累了，她接手。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:524
translate chinese lisa12b_b119a5b4:

    # "And when she is tired, I take over."
    "当她累了，我接手。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:528
translate chinese lisa12b_16d421dc:

    # "And when we're both tired, we slow down, but don't stop."
    "当我们都累了，我们会放慢节奏，但不会停下。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:532
translate chinese lisa12b_61bb6a0c:

    # "Until we regain our energy, and pick up the pace once more."
    "直到我们恢复精力，再次加快节奏。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:533
translate chinese lisa12b_2665d5a6:

    # "Fucking like it's our first time."
    "做爱时仿佛是第一次。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:534
translate chinese lisa12b_ffe7614e:

    # "Finally unleashing ourselves and allowing ourselves to fully enjoy each other."
    "终于彻底释放自我，任由彼此尽情享受。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:537
translate chinese lisa12b_3fa64a38:

    # "And we both cum."
    "我们双双高潮。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:541
translate chinese lisa12b_ebce4a14:

    # "And cum."
    "一次又一次。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:545
translate chinese lisa12b_ebce4a14_1:

    # "And cum."
    "一次又一次。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:549
translate chinese lisa12b_ebce4a14_2:

    # "And cum."
    "一次又一次。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:553
translate chinese lisa12b_380ff4bb:

    # "And before long, the sun is rising and we still haven't gone to sleep."
    "没过多久，朝阳已升起，而我们仍未入睡。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:557
translate chinese lisa12b_d41d8cd9_13:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_iloveyou.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_iloveyou.wav'

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:558
translate chinese lisa12b_14c552ae:

    # sp "I love you, [pcname]."
    sp "我爱你，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:559
translate chinese lisa12b_30ede8ed:

    # sp "I can barely move, but I love you."
    sp "我几乎动弹不得，但我爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:560
translate chinese lisa12b_8afddbd2:

    # "We hold each other. And finally, we allow ourselves to sink into a deep sleep."
    "我们紧紧相拥。最终，任由自己沉入深沉的睡眠。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:567
translate chinese lisa12b_8cd42ce7:

    # "A few hours later, we wake up, check out of the hotel and start driving back to reality."
    "几个小时后，我们醒来，退了房，开始开车返回现实。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:568
translate chinese lisa12b_72fa48a3:

    # sp "Last night was... just wow. One of the best nights of my life."
    sp "昨晚真是……太棒了。那是我人生中最美好的夜晚之一。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:569
translate chinese lisa12b_679e0af5:

    # sp "I'd love to continue this. To pursue this like a real relationship."
    sp "我很想继续下去。像一段真正的恋爱关系那样去经营。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:570
translate chinese lisa12b_7d0f7c74:

    # sp "But I'm worried what Suzy will think. I don't think we need to tell her just yet."
    sp "但我担心苏西会怎么想。我觉得暂时没必要告诉她。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:571
translate chinese lisa12b_5869066b:

    # sp "I don't think we should get too serious right now."
    sp "我觉得现在不该太认真。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:572
translate chinese lisa12b_962e3de8:

    # sp "You should definitely keep seeing other people. You're so young. Don't settle down with just one person yet. Don't do what I did."
    sp "你绝对应该继续和其他人约会。你还这么年轻。别现在就只和一个人定下来。别重蹈我的覆辙。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:573
translate chinese lisa12b_2ee0d222:

    # sp "But if you could make some time for me every once in a while, I'd really appreciate it."
    sp "但如果你能偶尔抽点时间陪我，我会非常感激。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:574
translate chinese lisa12b_6d410e83:

    # sp "And we'll just see where this whole thing goes."
    sp "至于这一切会走向何方，我们走着瞧吧。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:577
translate chinese lisa12b_7168094f:

    # "When we get home, we walk each other inside and she kisses me next to the stairs."
    "回到家后，我们互相搀着走进屋内，她在楼梯旁吻了我。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:578
translate chinese lisa12b_74c5ad4d:

    # "I know it's a sort of goodbye kiss, before things go back to normal."
    "我知道这算是一种告别之吻，之后一切又会恢复常态。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:579
translate chinese lisa12b_56a744dd:

    # sp "Love you."
    sp "爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:580
translate chinese lisa12b_93df423a:

    # pc "Love you too, [mom]."
    pc "我也爱你，[mom]。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:581
translate chinese lisa12b_921dbe9b:

    # "We pull away quickly when we hear Suzy's door open upstairs."
    "听到楼上苏茜的房门打开，我们赶紧分开。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:585
translate chinese lisa12b_b1a00209:

    # ss "Hey guys, how did it go? Was it super boring?"
    ss "嘿，你们俩，玩得怎么样？是不是超级无聊？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:586
translate chinese lisa12b_e7c30ea0:

    # sp "Yeah, pretty boring."
    sp "是啊，挺无聊的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:587
translate chinese lisa12b_633ddf1c:

    # sp "I'm exhausted though. Because of the trip. I'm going to head to bed early."
    sp "不过我累坏了。因为这趟旅行。我要早点睡了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:588
translate chinese lisa12b_9a9069c4:

    # ss "All right. Good night, Mom!"
    ss "好的。晚安，妈妈！"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:590
translate chinese lisa12b_3d2f734c:

    # ss "I can't believe you got suckered into going with her."
    ss "真不敢相信你居然被她忽悠去陪她了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa12.rpy:591
translate chinese lisa12b_34188b57:

    # pc "Yeah. It was pretty awful."
    pc "是啊。那简直糟透了。"

